<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:37:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Bitwarden 在 Windows 11 上添加了对密钥登录的支持</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/bitwarden-adds-support-for-passkey-login-on-windows-11</link><description>Bitwarden 宣布支持使用存储在管理器保管库中的密钥登录 Windows 11 设备，从而实现防网络钓鱼身份验证。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/bitwarden-adds-support-for-passkey-login-on-windows-11.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/bitwarden-adds-support-for-passkey-login-on-windows-11</guid></item><item><title>Windows 10 KB5075039 更新修复了损坏的恢复环境</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/windows-10-kb5075039-update-fixes-broken-recovery-environment</link><description>Microsoft 发布了适用于 Windows 10 的 KB5075039 Windows 恢复环境更新，以修复阻止某些用户访问恢复环境的长期存在的问题。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/windows-10-kb5075039-update-fixes-broken-recovery-environment.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/windows-10-kb5075039-update-fixes-broken-recovery-environment</guid></item><item><title>Amazon 为使用 GameLift 服务器的开发人员推出新的 DDoS 保护</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/amazon-introduces-new-ddos-protection-for-devs-using-gamelift-servers</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/amazon-introduces-new-ddos-protection-for-devs-using-gamelift-servers</guid></item><item><title>细胞类型：编码大脑的 BIOS</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cell-types-encoding-the-brains-bios</link><description>Patrick Mineault 撰写的出色的 Substack 文章介绍了细胞类型如何指定先天行为，以及为什么绘制专门用于引导先天行为的大脑区域（通过许多不同的细胞类型）可以引导我们建立更加一致的人工智能系统。这里提出了非常有说服力和优雅的论点！ [&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cell-types-encoding-the-brains-bios2.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 11:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cell-types-encoding-the-brains-bios</guid></item><item><title>调试量子处理器：新方法可精确定位逻辑运算期间的量子位错误</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/debugging-a-quantum-processor-new-method-pinpoints-qubit-errors-during-logical-operations</link><description>因斯布鲁克大学的研究人员与悉尼和滑铁卢的合作伙伴一起提出了一项研究&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/debugging-a-quantum-processor-new-method-pinpoints-qubit-errors-during-logical-operations.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 11:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/debugging-a-quantum-processor-new-method-pinpoints-qubit-errors-during-logical-operations</guid></item><item><title>Polycomb 复合物的染色质结合不平衡导致神经发育障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unbalanced-chromatin-binding-of-polycomb-complexes-drives-neurodevelopmental-disorders</link><description>多梳复合体错义突变导致的神经发育障碍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unbalanced-chromatin-binding-of-polycomb-complexes-drives-neurodevelopmental-disorders2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 11:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unbalanced-chromatin-binding-of-polycomb-complexes-drives-neurodevelopmental-disorders</guid></item><item><title>揭示压力细菌中的隐藏变量</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-hidden-variables-in-stressed-bacteria</link><description>细菌应激反应中的噪音常常被认为仅仅是随机性而被忽视。虽然真正的随机性存在，但许多变化反映了隐藏的变量——细胞状态、历史和微环境——这些变量现在才变得可测量。 Choudhary 和 Vincent 回顾了新兴工具，这些工具将偶然性与决定论分开，将微生物学推向更加机械化和预测性的框架。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unveiling-hidden-variables-in-stressed-bacteria2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 11:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-hidden-variables-in-stressed-bacteria</guid></item><item><title>为罕见癫痫儿童改变生活的药物被发现</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/life-changing-drug-identified-for-children-with-rare-epilepsy</link><description>根据伦敦大学学院（UCL）和大奥蒙德街医院领导的国际临床试验的结果，一种针对患有难以治疗的癫痫儿童的新实验性治疗方法是安全的，可以显着减少癫痫发作，帮助他们过上更健康、更快乐的生活。在发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/life-changing-drug-identified-for-children-with-rare-epilepsy.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 10:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/life-changing-drug-identified-for-children-with-rare-epilepsy</guid></item><item><title>葡萄糖代谢通过糖基化局部信号因子维持结直肠癌中异常的 STAT3 信号传导</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/glucose-metabolism-sustains-aberrant-stat3-signaling-in-colorectal-cancer-through-glycosylated-local-signaling-factors</link><description>降低葡萄糖利用率可以有效限制 STAT3 驱动的结直肠肿瘤生长。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glucose-metabolism-sustains-aberrant-stat3-signaling-in-colorectal-cancer-through-glycosylated-local-signaling-factors2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 10:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/glucose-metabolism-sustains-aberrant-stat3-signaling-in-colorectal-cancer-through-glycosylated-local-signaling-factors</guid></item><item><title>大脑如何在压力下抑制瘙痒</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-the-brain-suppresses-itch-during-stress</link><description>研究人员随后测试了这些压力激活的神经元是否直接影响瘙痒。 “我们进行了一些试点实验，令人惊讶的是，我们发现急性压力能够抑制急性瘙痒，”该研究的第一作者说。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-the-brain-suppresses-itch-during-stress2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 10:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-the-brain-suppresses-itch-during-stress</guid></item></channel></rss>